item.title: Prayer bpn6463 in Sesotho
item.description: Kea paka, Oho Molimo oa ka, hore U ntlholile ho U tseba le ho U sebeletsa, Kea paka hona joale hore kea fokola ‘me U matla, hore ke mofutsana ‘me U morui. Ha ho Molimo O mong kantle ho Uena, Mothusi litlokotsing, Ea-Phahametseng Tsohle. (Source category: Motšeare o moholo) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6463)
